#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:447
msgid ""
"Choose where the PayPal buttons should appear on the cart page, either above "
"or below the \"Proceed to Checkout\" button. This applies only to classic "
"cart templates, not the new Cart Blocks layout."
